{"tid":1929902,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"理大圍城四個月，勿忘。","createTime":"2020-03-17T08:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T10:13:08.000Z","uid":238660,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bddfca12d3625150ef2510b5a4627e38149258fc","tid":1929902,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"今日係理大之戰四個月，你還記得嗎？<br />\n<br />\n那群勢死捍衛大學多日的香港人；那群走上街頭徒步走向理大的香港人；那群呼喊著手足頂住呀加油的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n你還記得嗎？四個月前的中大之戰及理大之戰，鼓舞了多少人心，現在難道要冷卻在支那武漢肺疫？<br />\n<br />\n請你不忘抗爭，堅持到光復那天，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n#理大之戰 #毋忘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98563750dfb454d22151f6785b678ed58f335d9a","tid":1929902,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff66c5bde885d061b76e031113327aeea7ab4204","tid":1929902,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:25:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cb7949029e2587157a4d9fa683f2a71ca168452","tid":1929902,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4dc0c17f8f1c487e9dff33d2d71cff7a43860e9","tid":1929902,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"071952a5189363ee8329ae4a99922bc9dc9aadd8","tid":1929902,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:29:33.000Z","msg":"K."},{"pid":"29fea3477a74ecf44c84af8011e35f309c1f8e5d","tid":1929902,"uid":194363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:31:57.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"9d45d5771761c5a42b96664b581118408c186447","tid":1929902,"uid":326098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:32:49.000Z","msg":"推 never forget and forgive"},{"pid":"bc58186293d97f3f5f5d38d307acc76425b7d566","tid":1929902,"uid":141285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"